## **Rectors and Leadership**

Since its founding, the Edinburgh Academy has been led by a series of **Rectors**, including:
- **John Williams** (1824–1828, 1829–1847)
- **James Stephen Hodson** (1854–1869)
- **Robert Mackenzie** (1888–1901)
- **Barry Welsh** (2017–present)

Notable former staff include:
- **[D'Arcy Wentworth Thompson](/D%27Arcy_Wentworth_Thompson_(Galway))** (classicist)
- **[Arthur Pressland FRSE](/Arthur_John_Pressland)** (educational theorist)
- **[W. P. D. Wightman FRSE](/W._P._D._Wightman)** (Science Master)

